               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Hāymānota ʾabaw (fols. 2ra-25va)&#xD; II) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of
                     Mary” (fols. 25vb-117vb)&#xD; II-1) Introductory exhortation (fols.
                     25vb-26va)&#xD; II-2) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols.
                     27ra-31rb)&#xD; II-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... “I worship Thee...”
                     (fols. 31rb-31vb)&#xD; II-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām: 103 miracles (fols. 32ra-117vb),
                     possibly incomplete, fols. are misplaced.&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
